reviewText: I've always been a big fan of Anne of Green Gables, and I loved seeing this other series by LM Montgomery.
Fast delivery and was pleased with the product.
Too much of the occult in the stories.

Love this series. Just happened upon it, and I have really fallen for all the characters. Don't know if there are any more after season 4, they certainly left room for the possibility!
I sure hope so! Highly recommend!
It  is a great family show. No sex scenes, no foul language just a great clean family show.  Wish there were more of them.
